config BR2_PACKAGE_FINIT
	bool "finit"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBITE
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBUEV
	help
	  Finit is a small event based SysV init replacement with built-in
	  process supervision similar to that of its more famous cousins
	  daemontools and runit. Services are supervised and automatically
	  restarted if they fail.

	  http://troglobit.com/finit.html
